<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3961] Add Delete.setWriteToWAL functionality</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3961</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For puts, write to WAL can be disabled, but for deletes this functionality is missing. The regionserver internally already passes around a writeToWAL flag, but it is not possible to set this from the client.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The attached patch introduces this.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This changes the serialization format of Delete, so bumped up the version.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I verified manually that the WAL is indeed not growing when writeToWAL is set to false.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
